--------------------------------------------------------------
   =======================================================
   MEIGA - Simulations Framework for Astroparticle Physics
   =======================================================

                       G4LeadSimulator
                       ---------------
--------------------------------------------------------------


Application for simulating the muon tomography of a brick
of Lead using Scintillator Detectors.

The G4LeadSimulator.json contains a block of settings
for the simulation of a brick of lead:

"LeadBrick" :
  {
    "Simulate" : true,
    "Position" : [0, -15, 105],
    "Size"     : [20, 20, 10]
  }

Position and Size are given in cm.

If the brick simulation is disabled ("Simulate" : false),
this application is equivalent to G4HodoscopeSimulator.
 
For a more detailed description about the 
detectors see: src/Applications/G4HodoscopeSimulator/README


